♪Even the coldest winter feels warm♪

7
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:50,780
♪Since falling for you,
I only want your company♪

8
00:00:51,060 --> 00:00:54,940
♪You see through
all my sweet little schemes♪

9
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:57,340
♪What should I do?♪

10
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:06,100
[My Sassy Girl]

11
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,100
[Episode 8]

12
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,120
Alright,

13
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,760
I'll leave you two alone

14
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,680
to enjoy this beautiful moment.

15
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,400
Bye.

16
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:28,800
Nanyi,

17
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,920
now,

18
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,080
everything is clear.

19
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,040
Thinking back,

20
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,080
I realize I was also at fault.

21
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,320
I shouldn't have

22
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,080
jumped to conclusions

23
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,120
before understanding
the whole situation.

24
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,560
Does this mean

25
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,040
you forgive me?

26
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,040
So can we...?

27
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,520
Who said I forgave you?

28
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,320
The storybooks
about the faithless Lin Qingqiu

29
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,480
have been bestsellers
in Jinzhou for over a year.

30
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,360
What took you so long to find me?

31
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:05,960
After you left,

32
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,360
I fell seriously ill.

33
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,200
As soon as I recovered,

34
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,040
I started searching for you.

35
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:15,760
It was a while ago

36
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,040
that I saw your storybooks.

37
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,120
I then came to Jinzhou immediately.

38
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:23,460
♪Thinking of you,
the clouds look pink♪

39
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,080
Nanyi,

40
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:27,300
♪One bite, so sweet♪

41
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,080
let's get back together.

42
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,040
This time,

43
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,840
nothing will separate us.

44
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,240
Okay.

45
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:42,140
♪I want to draw
a love line on your palm♪

46
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:47,140
♪Extending it from your hand
all the way to my heart♪

47
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:53,420
♪Loving you
is like honey melting in the sun♪

48
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:57,740
♪Even the coldest winter feels warm♪

49
00:02:58,020 --> 00:03:03,100
♪Loving you,
I'm one hug away from being Queen♪

50
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:05,260
[Lu's Book Club]

51
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,680
You look fabulous

52
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:44,920
in that dress.

53
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,520
Nanyi,

54
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,960
I've always had bad luck.

55
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,680
Meeting you

56
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,080
is probably the luckiest thing
that's ever happened to me.

57
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,280
From the first moment I saw you,

58
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,040
I wanted to marry you.

59
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,760
Even though I've known you

60
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,680
for a shorter time than he has,

61
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,240
my love for you is no less.

62
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,400
You said you wanted to be

63
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,840
the greatest storyteller in Daling.

64
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,280
Then I want to be

65
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:19,480
the man standing behind Daling's

66
00:04:19,520 --> 00:04:20,560
greatest storyteller,

67
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,280
fully supporting you.

68
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,680
You said you couldn't move on.

69
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,760
That's fine.

70
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,120
I'll spend the rest of my life
helping you move on.

71
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,480
I, Fu Wenyuan,

72
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,720
have only one wish in this life.

73
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,520
That's to protect you, Lu Nanyi,

74
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,560
and keep you safe

75
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,560
and happy.

76
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:58,000
This is the deed to my property.

77
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,800
I know it might not matter to you,

78
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,360
but I don't know

79
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,400
what else I can give you

80
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,480
to show my sincerity.

81
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:10,480
Nanyi,

82
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,200
as long as you're unmarried,

83
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,320
I'll wait for you.

84
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,360
Fu Wenyuan,

85
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,200
the best thing

86
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,440
about coming to Jinzhou

87
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,520
was meeting you.

88
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,600
I mean it.

89
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,240
My dear friend,

90
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,720
you'll find someone better.

91
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:38,680
Don't worry.

92
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,800
No pressure.

93
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,840
I'll compete with him fairly.

94
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,240
Who knows who will win?

95
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,000
No!

96
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,840
Hurry up!

97
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,460
Get in there!

98
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,100
- Let me out!
- Get inside!

99
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,120
Quick!

100
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,320
Let me go!

101
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:38,700
[Bao Sheng, originally from the capital]

102
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:42,420
[Sun Qinjiu,
originally from the capital]

103
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:44,880
Look at this.

104
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,400
Bao Sheng and Sun Qinjiu

105
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,200
were both originally from the capital.

106
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:52,920
They moved

107
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,760
to Jinzhou to settle down ten years ago.

108
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,560
Does that mean

109
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,320
they might've known each other
for over a decade?

110
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,600
Yes,

111
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:02,720
it's very possible.

112
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,720
The black fish jade pendant

113
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,600
came from the tomb of Grand Preceptor Ji's
daughter in the capital.

114
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,040
There must be

115
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,840
some kind of connection.

116
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,960
[Jinzhou Bao Family Household Register]
Grand Preceptor Ji

117
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,440
was notoriously corrupt.

118
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,360
When his estates were seized,

119
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:22,040
only a small fraction
of his property was confiscated.

120
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,680
Rumor has it that before he died,

121
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,200
he hid all his treasures
in his daughter's tomb.

122
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,440
Whoever finds them

123
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,600
will become incredibly wealthy.

124
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,080
Do you think it's true?

125
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,200
We'll have to find out

126
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,560
through investigation.

127
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,080
Are you planning
to return to the capital?

128
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,720
Yes.

129
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,720
I'll report the case
to my superior today

130
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,000
and request permission
to return to the capital

131
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,240
and continue pursuing the real culprit.

132
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,040
I must find the truth
for the people of Jinzhou.

133
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:50,840
Also,

134
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,880
I want to take Nanyi with me.

135
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,240
I'll go with you both.

136
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:56,280
You...

137
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,440
You're all leaving?

138
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,800
Yin,

139
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,720
are you really going to the capital?

140
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,080
Of course.

141
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:16,800
Well,

142
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:17,840
then...

143
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,640
are you all packed?

144
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,960
What are you getting at?

145
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,240
Don't you

146
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,080
feel like

147
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,400
you're forgetting something?

148
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,320
Oh!

149
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,280
I forgot to take Chen and Xu with me.

150
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,320
Oh dear,

151
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,880
how could I forget you two?

152
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,480
Gong Beiyin!

153
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,240
You forgot to bring my heart!

154
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:15,960
Oh.

155
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,040
Then

156
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,360
I'll dig your heart out

157
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,560
and take it with me.

158
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,280
Go ahead!

159
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,640
You fool.

160
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,000
Take good care of your heart

161
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,080
and bring it

162
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,360
to the capital for me.

163
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:50,760
Yin,

164
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,200
are you saying

165
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,560
I can go with you to the capital?

166
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,200
You're such a hassle.

167
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:18,820
[Justice and Integrity]

168
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:25,880
Nanyi.

169
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,400
I heard from Yin

170
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,920
that you'd be heading back
to the capital for investigation.

171
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:36,640
Yes.

172
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:38,880
My superior has approved it.

173
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:42,120
There is a ten-year-old cold case
in the capital involving a red coffin.

174
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:45,280
Like Bao Sheng and Sun Qinjiu,
the victim was also from the capital,

175
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,800
so I've been ordered
to investigate these cases together.

176
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,440
An official will take over
my duties in Jinzhou temporarily

177
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:53,320
so I can focus
on my investigation in the capital.

178
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:56,760
Good.

179
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,400
These bizarre cases

180
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,400
do need a thorough investigation.

181
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,320
Well,

182
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,000
safe travels.

183
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,680
Nanyi,

184
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,840
I want you to come with me.

185
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,040
What for?

186
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,680
I have another reason

187
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,000
for going to the capital.

188
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,400
I'm going to break off my engagement

189
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,000
with Miss Wen.

190
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:39,760
Then,

191
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,160
I'll bring you home.

192
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,680
I never said I wanted
to go home with you.

193
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,160
Well, I don't have much to do lately.

194
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,080
A trip to the capital

195
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,840
might not be a bad idea.

196
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,360
Don't get the wrong idea.

197
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:05,840
I'm not going there for you.

198
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,040
Well,

199
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,680
it's been a year since I left home.

200
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,040
I should go back and visit.

201
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,120
Besides,

202
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,600
these cases are linked to my stories.

203
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:18,160
I do need closure.

204
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:19,440
Indeed.

205
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,080
Miss Lu

206
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,440
is a prominent storybook writer.

207
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,680
Her talent should be known

208
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,040
to the people of the capital.

209
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,400
Exactly.

210
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,240
With these cases unsolved,

211
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:32,960
I am willing

212
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,520
to accompany you to the capital

213
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,280
to uncover the truth

214
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,320
and bring justice to the deceased.

215
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,760
It's late and getting cold.

216
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:55,720
This will keep you warm.

217
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,360
Oh,

218
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,240
so you knew I would come.

219
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:05,080
Nanyi?

220
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:06,880
Nanyi?

221
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:08,800
Yes?

222
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,040
We've arrived in the capital.

223
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,880
Wake up.

224
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:12,480
Okay.

225
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,040
Just now, someone

226
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,320
was snoring

227
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,120
and drooling.

228
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,760
Now, they're feeling embarrassed?

229
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,880
As long as your engagement
with the Wen family isn't off,

230
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,880
you're still bound by it.

231
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,280
Nanyi,

232
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:48,960
I've sent

233
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,760
multiple letters to the Wen Residence
to break off the engagement,

234
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,440
but back then, I wasn't in the capital,

235
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:56,560
so I couldn't explain in person.

236
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,400
Once we arrive,

237
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,080
I'll go to the Wen Residence

238
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,800
and clear things up.

239
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:03,880
Tsk.

240
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,560
If you can't let go of Miss Wen,

241
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,720
there's no need to force yourself.

242
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:15,960
You're the only one I care about.

243
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:17,520
No one else

244
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,120
matters to me.

245
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,280
Come and take a look!

246
00:15:30,740 --> 00:15:31,740
What's going on?

247
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:33,160
Yeah, why are there so many soldiers?

248
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,260
What happened?

249
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,160
Sir,

250
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,280
we've arrived in the capital.

251
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,160
Keep going ahead

252
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,120
to the Jingzhao Office.

253
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:41,880
Sir,

254
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,920
we might not be able to get through.

255
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:51,400
Prepare a stool.

256
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:52,760
Something big must have happened.

257
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,480
Keep it down.

258
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,760
This man must be very important.

259
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:57,880
Don't worry.

260
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:10,480
Greetings, Your Highness!

261
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,580
Is he the young Prince of Anding?

262
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:15,240
Mr. Lin is the young prince?

263
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,280
Who sent you here?

264
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:19,520
The Prince ordered us
to escort you back to the mansion.

265
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,720
Oh no,

266
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,520
I hope I haven't offended him before.

267
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,320
Is it too late

268
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,360
to start flattering him now?

269
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:28,040
It's not too late
for you to run off now.

270
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,960
Is this my mother's idea?

271
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,680
We are just following orders.

272
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,000
Your Highness, please return
to the mansion with us.

273
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:37,240
It's probably about the engagement
with the Wen family again.

274
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:41,080
Qingqiu,

275
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:42,880
I've been away
from the capital for months.

276
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:44,040
I'd like to go home first.

277
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:45,240
Sure.

278
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:46,800
Qingqiu,

279
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:47,840
oh no,

280
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:48,440
sir,

281
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:49,680
I...

282
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:51,680
want to go with Miss Yin.

283
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:52,600
Okay.

284
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,920
Where should we meet later?

285
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,040
The Jingzhao Office.

286
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,640
Understood.

287
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,560
Send word

288
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,440
that I'm on official duty

289
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,680
and that I will return after I catch

290
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:04,720
the real culprit.

291
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,000
Yuechu,

292
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:07,320
let's go.

293
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,040
Yes.

294
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,240
No wonder

295
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,520
his family

296
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:32,440
doesn't approve of him
being with Miss Lu.

297
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,400
He's a young prince!

298
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:36,720
Shut up.

299
