How dare you, a mere prefect of Jinzhou,

302
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,680
not kneel

303
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,640
before the illustrious Vice Mr. Lu

304
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,480
of the Jingzhao Office?

305
00:17:58,680 --> 00:17:59,600
Outrageous.

306
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:03,160
My young master
is the young Prince of Anding.

307
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:07,060
