compared to your grandiosity, Mr. Lu.

312
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,640
Why is this vice minister

313
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:25,560
giving you a hard time?

314
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:28,120
